      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR WALLY (1) struggled to get involved last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won easily by 4.5 lengths at this track (25.13) beating PACKHAM PUNCH in a Grade 5 on June 14. The form out of his last race has been franked. Should bounce back. CASH CRUISE (8) hit the frame latest (25.18) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has two wins already from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. BENNY TRICK (7) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 450m. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. One of the key runners again. HEAR THE CROW (2) missed the frame latest (26.33) when sixth over 450m at this track in a Grade 5. Has already won two times from this draw.",
